{"tid":1803232,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"<Netflix> 2020 1月1 各方熱議新劇   （彌 賽 亞 Messiah ）","createTime":"2019-12-30T05:09:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T04:49:32.000Z","uid":240448,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"1862d2b512aca1ae9d762ccd1955d1a22110704d","tid":1803232,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T05:09:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qMcSSqJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqMcSSqJ.png&h=16d42e05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講述一名神秘宗教領袖突在中東崛起，並遭美國聯邦調查局（CIA）全球追殺。<em><ins><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">劇情引發各方熱議，甚至有人要連署抵制。</span></strong></ins></em><br />\n<br />\n創作者裴從尼（Michael Petroni）告訴法新社：「是的，這部影集啟發性十足，充滿挑釁。但挑釁不是冒犯。」<br />\n<br />\n「彌賽亞」（Messiah）將在明年1月1日上線，<ins><strong><em><span style=\"color: violet;\">想像當類似宗教領袖出現時，他的訊息在充斥「假新聞」與24小時新聞快報的世界裡，透過社群媒體快速傳播，現代社會將如何回應。</span></em></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n由比利時演員麥赫迪戴比（Mehdi Dehbi）飾演的主角，究竟是真正的彌賽亞、邪惡政治特務或單純是個神棍，則是整部影集的核心。<br />\n<br />\n裴從尼承認，他萌生的這個點子讓Netflix非常「緊張」。他說：「這是如此放肆的概念，你知道嗎？你看了試播集，這傢伙要跟2000名巴勒斯坦敘利亞人遊行橫跨以色列邊界。」<br />\n<br />\n他的構想包括以相當大的成本，復刻耶路撒冷的伊斯蘭教名寺聖殿山（Temple Mount）的一部分，包含穆斯林認為先知穆罕默德升天之處的神聖圓頂清真寺（Dome of the Rock）。<br />\n<br />\n在這些象徵性地點進行拍攝向來遙不可及，特別是這些場景出現的一幕充斥暴力血腥，但裴從尼堅稱這部影集「不是為了冒犯任何人」。他說：「不是說我樂見反彈，我們預料會有很多意見圍繞這部影集，很多辯論，我希望激起很多討論。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://請願網站Change.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%AB%8B%E9%A1%98%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99Change.org&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkYuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=6b5bbf7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">請願網站Change.org</a>上，已經有人呼籲抵制這部影集，形容它是「是邪惡的反伊斯蘭宣傳」。<br />\n<br />\n「彌賽亞」影集沒有表明這名宗教領袖的信仰為何，而裴從尼拒絕從自己的信仰中取材，但影集的另外兩名製作人、夫妻檔柏奈特（Mark Burnett）和陶尼（Roma Downey）有基督教背景。<br />\n<br />\n「彌賽亞」的首部預告片本月稍早釋出，引來部分穆斯林觀眾奚落，說主角名字麥西哈（Al-Masih）在伊斯蘭神學中意指偽救世主（Dajjal），也就是基督教中的反基督（Antichrist）。（譯者：侯文婷/核稿：劉文瑜）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vWoZxqO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvWoZxqO.jpg&h=01c6c960&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mxBPUD9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmxBPUD9.jpg&h=6c494759&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cfoboxv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcfoboxv.jpg&h=58c2610e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n湯摩爾&middot;席勒飾亞維蘭 (Aviram) <br />\n<br />\n約翰&middot;歐提茲飾菲利斯&middot;伊奎羅 (Felix Iguero)<br />\n<br />\n梅琳達&middot;佩姬&middot;漢米爾頓飾安娜&middot;伊奎羅 (Anna Iguero)<br />\n<br />\n瑟法妮雅&middot;拉維&middot;歐文飾雷貝嘉&middot;伊奎羅 (Rebecca Iguero)<br />\n<br />\n薩伊德&middot;艾爾阿拉米飾伽百利 (Jibril) <br />\n<br />\n珍&middot;亞當斯飾米利暗&middot;簡尼利 (Miriam Keneally)<br />\n<br />\n威爾&middot;崔佛飾威廉&middot;梅瑟 (Will Mathers)<br />\n<br />\n法瑞斯&middot;蘭杜爾西飾薩莫 (Samer)<br />\n<br />\n德蒙&middot;穆拉尼飾楊恩 (Young) 總統<br />\n<br />\n鮑&middot;布里吉斯飾艾德蒙&middot;迪蓋 (Edmund De Guilles)<br />\n<br />\n菲利普&middot;貝克&middot;霍爾 (Philip Baker Hall) 飾薩曼&middot;卡茲 (Zelman Katz)"},{"pid":"20437805209bc92512d6c248f6173cee2f680a66","tid":1803232,"uid":240448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T05:11:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">一名男子（麥賀比&middot;戴比 (Mehdi Dehbi) 飾）透過擾亂社會秩序獲得國際關注，中情局探員夏娃&middot;蓋勒 (Eva Geller)（蜜雪兒&middot;摩納漢 (Michelle Monaghan) 飾）發現有關他的情資，便著手調查他的底細。追隨他的群眾越來越多，信徒都宣稱他能施展奇蹟，全球媒體亦逐漸被這位富有魅力的人物給深深吸引。蓋勒必須盡快解開圍繞在這位男子身上的謎團：他究竟真的是位聖人，還是將摧毀全球地緣政治秩序的危險騙徒？隨著故事開展，多個觀點將會交織呈現，其中包括以色列情報員（湯摩爾&middot;席勒 (Tomer Sisley) 飾）、德州牧師（約翰&middot;歐提茲 (John Ortiz) 飾）、牧師女兒（瑟法妮雅&middot;拉維&middot;歐文 (Stefania LaVie Owen) 飾）、巴勒斯坦難民（薩伊德&middot;艾爾阿拉米 (Sayyid El Alami) 飾），以及追蹤相關報導的記者（珍&middot;亞當斯 (Jane Adams) 飾）。影集的演員陣容亦包括梅琳達&middot;佩姬&middot;漢米爾頓 (Melinda Page Hamilton)、威爾&middot;崔佛 (Wil Traval)、法瑞斯&middot;蘭杜爾西 (Fares Landoulsi)、德蒙&middot;穆拉尼 (Dermot Mulroney) 與鮑&middot;布里吉斯 (Beau Bridges)。<br />\n<br />\n此影集由《偷書賊》(The Book Thief) 編劇麥可&middot;帕佐尼 (Michael Petroni) 創作，《V 怪客》(V for Vendetta) 導演詹姆斯&middot;麥克特格 (James McTeigue) 與《矯正人生》(Rectify) 導演凱特&middot;伍茲 (Kate Woods) 共同執導，監製則由帕佐尼、麥克特格、《替身》(The Double) 製作人安德魯&middot;黛 (Andrew Deane) 以及《聖經故事》(The Bible Series) 和《賓漢》(Ben Hur) 的製作人馬克&middot;布奈特 (Mark Burnett) 和蘿瑪&middot;道尼 (Roma Downey) 聯合擔綱。Netflix 原創影集《彌賽亞》(Messiah) 是部發人深省又充滿懸疑的驚悚劇集，探討影響力與信仰在社群媒體時代的力量。</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9cc5bbc0bd2b8379e89a834d2e4c437f86568abc","tid":1803232,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T05:13:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Ap2vd2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Ap2vd2.png&h=7250f9b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a30e1b13e094b8f5b8355682be8d2309a1f2a7c7","tid":1803232,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T05:14:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mjLWuzGVyew\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmjLWuzGVyew&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkYuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=fcc6b9b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mjLWuzGVyew</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NPe_RiJM7jU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNPe_RiJM7jU&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkYuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=23f1efec\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NPe_RiJM7jU</a>"},{"pid":"5c99e22f1181e5dd520fcc3cdbad3bb7167942c0","tid":1803232,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T05:15:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/R_SgtQBpMh0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FR_SgtQBpMh0&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkYuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=53faa6dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/R_SgtQBpMh0</a>"},{"pid":"2f0fbdaeb2993b4c7998d843661ea41628f7d260","tid":1803232,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:49:47.000Z","msg":"有無人準備睇呀"},{"pid":"1852b33092691be93fa696e50abdaefe10bc592f","tid":1803232,"uid":48869,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T07:19:21.000Z","msg":"題材幾好"},{"pid":"442fdbab1ca7046005222e5e7783e06a55ee40bc","tid":1803232,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1852b33092691be93fa696e50abdaefe10bc592f","tid":1803232,"uid":48869,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T07:19:21.000Z","msg":"題材幾好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T07:32:31.000Z","msg":"期待緊"},{"pid":"9651ee60b23b1974f3f45eb22e353b6f1f924837","tid":1803232,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T07:42:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/messiahnetflix/status/1211346142841188353?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmessiahnetflix%2Fstatus%2F1211346142841188353%3Fs%3D21&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkYuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=3b103081\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmessiahnetflix%2Fstatus%2F1211346142841188353%3Fs%3D21&h=188e17e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/messiahnetflix/status/1211346142841188353?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"e8230abc28bf153c0903be280109d871967b53d7","tid":1803232,"uid":240448,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:07:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WQBlkF5lUuc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWQBlkF5lUuc&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkYuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=d7e203b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WQBlkF5lUuc</a>"},{"pid":"06c6da82270335a70c31c16805b0a2b911f1051d","tid":1803232,"uid":842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:26:22.000Z","msg":"有冇人睇咗？"},{"pid":"6a5beecd7acdebaaef39eb070376095f1a209c0a","tid":1803232,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06c6da82270335a70c31c16805b0a2b911f1051d","tid":1803232,"uid":842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:26:22.000Z","msg":"有冇人睇咗？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:30:37.000Z","msg":"準